00:23:39.918 --> 00:23:41.521
Potato field.

392
00:23:41.545 --> 00:23:42.438
And?

393
00:23:42.462 --> 00:23:44.413
Bathroom.

394
00:23:44.882 --> 00:23:45.858
Kitchen.

395
00:23:45.882 --> 00:23:48.835
And? If you don't see me there?

396
00:23:49.302 --> 00:23:51.420
I should call you.

397
00:23:52.639 --> 00:23:54.382
