410
00:24:33.847 --> 00:24:36.424
"Come empty, return empty."

411
00:24:36.641 --> 00:24:39.287
I, Oh Tae-soo, will come empty-handed...

412
00:24:39.311 --> 00:24:40.454
<i><font color="#ffff00">Encountering A New Era, A New Person</font></i>

413
00:24:40.478 --> 00:24:42.331
...and leave empty-handed.

414
00:24:42.355 --> 00:24:43.583
I see.

415
00:24:43.607 --> 00:24:46.627
That was Assemblyman Oh's
principle when it comes to politics.

416
00:24:46.651 --> 00:24:48.603
If he declares candidacy, that is.

417
00:24:48.862 --> 00:24:53.301
Let's look forward to seeing
the rise of a new political leader.

418
00:24:53.325 --> 00:24:56.679
This time, I'd like to ask a casual question.

419
00:24:56.703 --> 00:25:01.407
Who gives you the most strength when you need...

420
00:25:01.541 --> 00:25:03.436
<i>What did you just say?</i>

421
00:25:03.460 --> 00:25:06.662
<i>You want the money back?</i>

422
00:25:07.297 --> 00:25:10.610
