425
00:25:16.389 --> 00:25:19.216
<i>and ended up putting us in danger.</i>

426
00:25:19.351 --> 00:25:21.621
<i>This is a breach of contract.</i>

427
00:25:21.645 --> 00:25:25.958
I already know the hit-and-run
accident and suicide were in the contract.

428
00:25:25.982 --> 00:25:28.628
As soon as I received a huge
amount of money in the bank,

429
00:25:28.652 --> 00:25:31.130
I got a call about my husband's death.

430
00:25:31.154 --> 00:25:34.607
And the day after that,
I received his suicide note.

431
00:25:34.658 --> 00:25:36.761
<i>It was all written there.</i>

432
00:25:36.785 --> 00:25:40.514
<i>Where he got the money, who made him do it,</i>

433
00:25:40.538 --> 00:25:43.783
<i>and why he had to take his own life.</i>

434
00:25:44.125 --> 00:25:46.118
<i>Where is...</i>

435
00:25:46.211 --> 00:25:47.855
<i>Mr. Yang's suicide note?</i>

436
00:25:47.879 --> 00:25:51.582
If you lay a finger on my child or me,

437
00:25:52.175 --> 00:25:55.252
<i>that note will be sent to the police.</i>

438
00:25:55.679 --> 00:25:58.089
<i>I must save myself too.</i>

439
00:26:02.727 --> 00:26:04.428
All right.

440
00:26:05.188 --> 00:26:07.890
Would you like to continue watching?

441
00:26:08.566 --> 00:26:11.796
It took me a lot of effort...

442
00:26:11.820 --> 00:26:14.215
to find all these.

443
00:26:14.239 --> 00:26:15.940
Do you know that?

444
00:26:17.742 --> 00:26:19.438
Apparently at the time of the accident,

445
00:26:19.462 --> 00:26:23.766
Kang-ho was asleep in the car.

446
00:26:23.790 --> 00:26:25.601
How does that make any sense?

447
00:26:25.625 --> 00:26:27.478
He'd just cut ties with his mother,

448
00:26:27.502 --> 00:26:29.329
but managed to sleep peacefully afterward?

449
00:26:29.353 --> 00:26:34.766
Does this mean Kang-ho is
the worst jerk in history?

450
00:26:34.884 --> 00:26:37.697
Or did someone slip him...

451
00:26:37.721 --> 00:26:40.366
sleeping pills or something?

452
00:26:40.390 --> 00:26:42.008
Oh, right.

453
00:26:42.809 --> 00:26:46.747
The day before the accident, your daughter...

454
00:26:46.771 --> 00:26:50.084
