462
00:27:26.519 --> 00:27:28.304
Do you remember...

463
00:27:28.355 --> 00:27:30.291
Choi Hae-sik?

464
00:27:30.315 --> 00:27:31.667
Choi... Who?

465
00:27:31.691 --> 00:27:33.127
Back in 1987,

466
00:27:33.151 --> 00:27:34.628
during the urban improvement,

467
00:27:34.652 --> 00:27:38.132
the man who was running
a pig farm in Bongu-dong.

468
00:27:38.156 --> 00:27:40.384
That Choi Hae-sik.

469
00:27:40.408 --> 00:27:43.262
Goodness, I don't even
remember someone I met yesterday.

470
00:27:43.286 --> 00:27:45.556
A man from 30 years ago? Anyway, what about him?

471
00:27:45.580 --> 00:27:49.450
Do you know how my daughter
came to meet Choi Kang-ho?

472
00:27:50.085 --> 00:27:52.563
My daughter was arrested by him...

473
00:27:52.587 --> 00:27:55.274
for carrying illegal drugs.

474
00:27:55.298 --> 00:27:56.734
