to see if she was conscious,

516
00:30:07.597 --> 00:30:09.742
then a passerby saw it and made a report.

517
00:30:09.766 --> 00:30:13.802
He was soon arrested on
the scene by nearby officers.

518
00:30:15.897 --> 00:30:17.916
<i><font color="#ffa07a">Livestock Industry Permit
